Fórmula

formula <- trip_duration ~ Month +
  Day +
  Hour +
  #Minute +
  Weekday +
  vendor_id +
  #passenger_count +
  passenger_count_2 +
  store_and_fwd_flag +
  Distance

Regressão Linear

lm <- lm(formula, train)

Árvore de decisão

rpart <- rpart(formula, train)
